It carries the diagnosis's closing keyword ("interrogating whether she deserved to be there") into the origin story and answers the reader's implicit "where did this come from?" before dropping into Brenham. Matches the piece's short-standalone-line rhythm; no em-dashes, no AI tells, no voice drift.

